    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed across all five COU operating points with results demonstrating hemolysis index below clinical threshold at 90th percentile. Validation metric u_val satisfied at all operating points. The assurance package is accepted for regulatory submission. Note: a screening sensitivity study was conducted and is described in the technical report; the structured sensitivity analysis artifact has not been linked to this package but is available upon request.",
